00:11:48,360 --> 00:11:50,040
 I just wanna kind of forget about it all for a moment.

287
00:11:50,040 --> 00:11:52,680
 I just wanna kind of retreat into my own little world.

288
00:11:52,680 --> 00:11:55,440
 I can see this, I can feel this at times.

289
00:11:55,440 --> 00:11:58,240
 Like I'm just gonna not let anyone actually know

290
00:11:58,240 --> 00:12:00,760
 kind of what I really believe or really think about that

291
00:12:00,760 --> 00:12:02,280
 because I just wanna kind of like,

292
00:12:02,280 --> 00:12:04,120
 just get on with everything.

293
00:12:04,120 --> 00:12:07,240
 So here's what I want you to do, first of all.

294
00:12:07,240 --> 00:12:09,080
 I want you to look at these four models

295
00:12:09,080 --> 00:12:12,000
 that church history has predominantly embraced.

296
00:12:12,000 --> 00:12:14,440
 And I want you to think about your time right now

297
00:12:14,440 --> 00:12:16,520
 dealing with your social media feeds,

298
00:12:16,520 --> 00:12:18,600
 seeing the stuff that's happening in the world,

299
00:12:18,600 --> 00:12:19,440
 seeing all the things

300
00:12:19,440 --> 00:12:21,280
 that we're wrestling with globally right now.

